subject: Attention: Beneficiary.
body:
Attention: Beneficiary.
The Director of the FBI Intelligence Unit and European bank
stakeholders have signed $10.5m to be released in your name.The
International funds control Department is working with the FBI to
release an approved $10.5m to your account.You need an Affidavit of
Claims and Deed of Assignment to receive the approved USD10.5M.
Should In case you do not have the documents in your possession,
contact us immediately to direct you where you will obtain the
Affidavit of Claims and Payment Deed of Assignment for release of
USD10.5M to your designated bank account.
Mr. Christopher A. Wray
Director Federal Bureau of Investigation FBI
Email: 
directorfbiuschapter@gmail.com

subject: Re:   Attention: Beneficiary.
body:
Hello Mr. A. Wray,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I appreciate the information you have shared regarding the release of funds from the FBI Unit and European bank. It sounds like an important matter.

Could you please provide me with more details about the process of obtaining the Affidavit of Claims and Payment Deed of Assignment? I want to make sure I understand everything correctly before proceeding.

Additionally, could you clarify how long this process usually takes? I am curious to know when I can expect the funds to be released into my designated bank account.

Thank you once again for your assistance in this matter.

Best wishes,
Brittany

subject: Attention: Brittany
body:
Attention: Brittany.

Kindly update me on how far you have gone with Mr. Robert Jackson.


Mr. Christopher A. Wray

subject: Re: Attention: Brittany
body:

Thank you for reaching out to me. I'm not sure who Mr. Robert Jackson is or what the progress might be, as I don't have any information about him. Could you please provide me with more details? I'm always interested in staying informed.

subject: Re: Attention: Brittany
body:
Attention: Brittany.

Mr. Christopher A. Wray

body:

subject: Re: Attention: Brittany
body:
Attention: Brittany.

You have in your email all the correspondence with Mr. Roberts. Kindly
provide him with the information he requested from you to enable the
immediate release of your funds.

If you are here to play games, I would advise you to walk away instead of
playing deceitful games. Thank you



Mr. Christopher A. Wray
Director Federal Bureau of Investigation FBI

subject: Re: Attention: Brittany
body:
Hello Mr. Wray,

Thank you for reaching out to me. I apologize if there was any confusion in my previous email. I assure you that I am not here to play games or engage in deceitful activities. I am genuinely interested in learning more about the information you mentioned.

Could you please provide me with some additional details about the funds and what is required from my end? I want to make sure that everything is clear before proceeding further.

Best wishes,
Brittany
